description:
**Role Description**
 Role Proficiency:




 Act creatively to develop applications and select appropriate technical options optimizing application development maintenance and performance by employing design patterns and reusing proven solutions account for others' developmental activities




 JD for




* 7\\+ years of BO Developer on Oracle DB with strong experience in SQL and PLSQL.
* Strong experience in Oracle DB.
* Strong experience in building BO Universes in UDT and IDT on Oracle tables/Schemas with SQL and PLSQL programing.
* Strong experience in building Schemas, Linked universes, create joins between tables, create alias tables, create contexts, and solve loops in schemas.
* Strong experience in reporting tools like Crystal reports and WebI. Any other reporting tools experience is a plus.
* Data extraction, transformation and load (ETL) scripting;
* Proficient with SQL and Entity Relationship diagrams;
* Strong experience on PL/SQL scripting;
* Experience in developing and maintaining Business Object reports, universe and metadata;
* Experience in migration of universe, users, groups etc Business Objects Reports from lower versions to higher versions using Import Wizard.
* Experience in CMC/CMS/CCM to manage few of the Admin activities individually is a plus
* Experience in Universe creation with strong data modelling and data architecture experience;
* Develop data queries for analyzing source data;
* Excellent business communications and consultative skills;
* Experience with developing report prototypes and fine tune report deliverables;


**Skills**
 Crystal Reports,SAP,Business Objects
